'''Argeleb''' is [[Sindarin]] for "Silver King" (from ''[[ar]]'', "royal", and ''[[celeb]]'', "silver") and can refer to:
* [[Argeleb I]] ({{TA|1226}} - {{TA|1356|n}}), seventh [[Kings of Arthedain|King]] of [[Arthedain]].
* [[Argeleb II]] ({{TA|1473}} - {{TA|1670|n}}), tenth [[Kings of Arthedain|King]] of [[Arthedain]].
